      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>Graphoris 1.0.4</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Fix: restore active-state highlight on canvas header</li>
          <li>Fix: save dialog loop and table reactivity issues</li>
          <li>Fix: 3D marker size rendering bug</li>
          <li>Fix: data table dark mode and multi-row delete</li>
